---
title: Double Glazed Chermoula Beef & Veggie Couscous with Garlic Yoghurt
description: A sweet honey glaze on chermoula-spiced beef strips? We say yes please! Feast your eyes on this delectable dinner, with a colourful veggie-speckled couscous acting as a fluffy bed for all of that juicy, beefy goodness. All you need is a dollop of garlic yoghurt for a touch of tang!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/673fb0e55915ccdf06c687e7-1db7c657.jpeg
